narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Ocean Partnership for Children Inc. is a Case Manager/Care Coordinator provider based in Brick, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $66.5M in Medicaid payments across 74K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $66.5M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
